{"tid":1632651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［入嚟討論］和理非週","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:30:15.000Z","uid":27026,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"86340a1b4b93aa38c3fd525e344685d95f75aef6","tid":1632651,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:23:55.000Z","msg":"政府揀係星期五，仲要係三連假嘅前夕推蒙面法，一定有佢原因。<br />\n<br />\n佢地一定知道蒙面法唔會有用，仲會引起更大嘅民憤，目的係咩？我認為就係想勇武繼續升溫、繼續私了。佢地都話希望市民同勇武割蓆，就係造就分化。特別係呢三日假，黑警都預告埋會有危險，呢個明顯就佢係地個圈套。<br />\n<br />\n更絕嘅係，佢地話希望蒙面法有助減少暴力事件，如果我地又行返和理非果套，又會比佢地話蒙面法有用。簡直進可攻、退可守，立於不敗之地。仲可以搞到連登好似依家咁分化晒，諗呢條橋嘅人好撚醒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日不斷有裝修同神獸，更加令國際嘅輿論風向帶向批抨手足過火，令美國人權法可能受到阻滯。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以，我建議：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">行返一星期嘅和理非週末</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個週末可以：<br />\n<br />\n比勇武休息、文宣解釋、仲有全民口罩週、唱國歌、懲罰黃店、摺紙鷂......等等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比國際見到我地對蒙面法嘅不滿，特別一定要全民戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n至於聽日嘅十八區開花，我建議可以轉做和理非（只係建議，手足無論做咩都唔會割，同時係我自己私心唔想有手足被拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n我冇咩開過po，都係留言多，可能有人會覺得係帶風向，但係希望手足可以諗下我講嘅有冇道理，然後一齊討論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"23b5dfc57e3fa4440d28d095da6c831793d16bf3","tid":1632651,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbd8574bba2c26763d94828dd19b9694e53ce1c","tid":1632651,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:39.000Z","msg":"好快沉底自推1/10"},{"pid":"f493212cb1421a6a350f0c0ad29ff816f64abfcb","tid":1632651,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"好快沉底自推2/10"},{"pid":"8c8f488a3bbccb01f0ac801438a8424e2dc71448","tid":1632651,"uid":90421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:25:17.000Z","msg":"和勇一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不分和勇，入左黎先，攞番國際輿論又唔駛不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632602-\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632602-</a> 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ce8c3b1e341e3963562971c809a9cd9087790dd","tid":1632651,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:25:51.000Z","msg":"好快沉底自推3/10"},{"pid":"c187b1365ea5b8c471ba31e691c1d7cbb1a2e3d8","tid":1632651,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:26:02.000Z","msg":"今晚既連登超多兩極分化, 充滿負能量, 玩住TWITTER先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【3分鐘懶人包】依家整埋bot 教你玩 twitter, 連翻譯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594532</a><br />\n<br />\n進階<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1496781/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1496781/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1482058/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1482058/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1600121/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1600121/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1489008/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1489008/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602587/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602587/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f8e4f7f1b9940398ff2b2d1253ee60a5cb39555a","tid":1632651,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:26:18.000Z","msg"